                            Jab is lot mein sirf 5 minute bache honge, hum aapko push notification bhejenge. Koi bid miss mat karo!
                        </p>
                        
                        <button class="w-full bg-white text-red-700 py-4 rounded-2xl text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest shadow-xl hover:bg-gray-50 active:scale-95 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
